body:
Reproducer : 

```systemverilog
typedef struct packed {
    logic [7:0] f;
} sbus_t;

module test_top();

    sbus_t sig;

    initial
        $display("%d %d %d", $left(sig.f), $right(sig.f), $bits(sig.f));

endmodule
```

```
$ iverilog -g2012 test.sv -o test && ./test
         x          x          8
```

